1
00:00:00,098 --> 00:00:02,122
The Candy Kings
糖果国王

2
00:00:02,145 --> 00:00:05,722
Once candy was not made for children.
以前糖果不是为儿童做的

3
00:00:05,764 --> 00:00:09,952
In one country, almost 5000 years ago,
在一个国家  近5000年前

4
00:00:09,985 --> 00:00:12,983
candy was made only for kings.
糖果只为国王而做

5
00:00:13,011 --> 00:00:17,072
Today, children are the candy kings.
如今  孩子们是糖果国王

6
00:00:17,105 --> 00:00:19,825
Have you ever eaten licorice?
你吃过甘草吗

7
00:00:19,863 --> 00:00:23,825
People in ancient times ate licorice, too.
人们在古代也吃甘草

8
00:00:23,863 --> 00:00:28,023
They did think of licorice as candy at first.
一开始他们认为甘草是糖果

9
00:00:28,051 --> 00:00:31,760
They ate licorice to keep them strong and well.
他们吃甘草来保持强壮和健康

10
00:00:31,792 --> 00:00:36,776
In some countries, people ate licorice to make them beautiful!
在一些国家  人们吃了甘草使他们变得漂亮

11
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:42,409
Later, people ate it just because it tasted good!
后来  人们吃它只是因为它味道好

12
00:00:42,456 --> 00:00:48,235
All candy was made by hand until 1845.
直到1845年  所有糖果是手工做的,

13
00:00:48,254 --> 00:00:52,701
In that year, a man made a candy machine.
那一年  一个男人做了一个糖果机

14
00:00:52,729 --> 00:00:58,202
By the 1900s, candy was sold all over the world.
1900年代  糖果被销往世界各地

15
00:00:58,235 --> 00:01:06,338
Today, candy companies say a person eats from 15 to 30 pounds of candy a year.
如今  糖果公司说一个人一年要吃15到30磅的糖果

16
00:01:06,381 --> 00:01:10,927
More than 2000 different kinds of candy are made!
制作了超过2000个不同种类的糖果

17
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:15,082
How many kinds do you eat, candy king?
你吃了多少种  糖果国王

